body.p:
The font_size represents the font size in em units. You can use this
      value to change the style of the
      element:font-size:attr(font_size, em);

The complete CSS rule
      is:para{
 display:block;
 background-color:attr(bg_color, color);
 font-size:attr(font_size, em);
 margin:attr(space, em);
}
